A CALCULATOR WITH SEVEN SEGMENT DISPLAY USING PYTHON
_____________
|DESCRIPTION|
-------------
This application performs basic arthemetic operations along with some intermediate level unary operations.
All this is accomplished along with a GUI and a working Seven Segment display.

I have used The Pygame module, and basic object oriented design.

In this project i have learned basic object oriented design.
________________________________
|IF YOU WANT TO RUN THE PROGRAM|
--------------------------------
If you want to runt his file make sure you have Python 3.10.1, with pygame installed. Also, make sure the name of the image assets are named as i have named them.

FEEL FREE TO USE THIS CODE IN ANY WAY YOU DESIRE AND ANY CRITIQUES ARE WELCOMED